title: [Archeth's Armory]
[Archeth's Outfitting]
[Archeth's General Store]
description: A tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the dark oak walls, and a deep red stucco ceiling rises overhead.  An iron candelabra sits in one corner of a stained oak floor.  There is a low wrought iron table on one side of the shop and an iron-banded wooden chest on the other.

Navy blue rugs bordered with braided gold rope and bright white anchors cushion the long hallway as it stretches to the east and west.  Wrought iron rings dangle from the ceiling and hold aloft glass-fronted lanterns that shed bright yellow light and dispel all surrounding shadows.  Standing opposite each other, a windowed blue door has the words, "Office of the Curator," etched into its glass, while a windowed brown door has the words, "Office of the Realtor," etched into its glass.
